Ford to move production of Focus, C-Max from Michigan Assembly


July 9, 2015 @ 2:35 pm


Comments


Email



  







		SHARE 


Facebook 
Twitter 
LinkedIn 
Google+ 




0
Shares
















Manufacturing
Ford
Michigan
